He indicates the entrance to the stream.

Mustex: It's and entrance to an underground stream.
Rhesus is pretty sure we can follow it out all the way
to the ocean. By the way Rhesus how are we going to
get it under.

Rhesus: We can probably won't need more than 1 air
tank for a sub because the trips won't be as long as
in space we can use the rest as ballask tanks. I'll
rig it up to do so when it's in the water

Mustex: Great. Now we just need to get it in the
water. Could you help us get it into position? Facing
that way.

He points west.
